text: Staffs Joe and Kim are excellent and helped address some purchase concerns promptly and as committed..their shirts are of good quality and price reasonable.first time wearer of crocodile so had a positive experience with their cut and material.

The guy staff is super rude.

The auntie we met the last time is much much better in service and product knowledge.
They got the best deal in the town, I am impressed with the customer service and the pricing.
